~c~Protections_tooltip: ~r~[Zablokowano]~c~ zdobądź dostęp do zabezpieczeń anty modderskich kupując XenMenu ~b~[VIP]!
Never Dragged_tooltip: Sprawia że nikt nie może wyciągnąć z pojazdu.
Off The Radar_tooltip: Ukrywa Cię z radaru, aby inni cię nie widzieli
Invisibility_tooltip: Sprawia że jesteś niewidoczny dla innych graczy.
Ghost Rider_tooltip: Pozostawia za tobą ślad w postaci efektów cząsteczkowych.
Death By Fire_tooltip: Zapal się i zgiń jak na stosie!
Scenarios_tooltip: Bardziej zaawansowane animacje czasami posiadającymi przedmioty, np. granie na gitarze.
Random Variations_tooltip: Gdy włączone, za każdym razem zmienia twój model na jego losową wersję.
Attachments_player_tooltip: Attach (or detach) various objects to the selected player.
Attachments_lobby_tooltip: Attach (or detach) various objects to everyone in this session.
Malicious_tooltip: Features such as Explode lobby, etc.
Attacks_tooltip: Features that may harm/kill the selected player, for example "Explode Player".
Vehicle_tooltip: Features that may affect the vehicle this player is using.
~c~Drop Options_tooltip: Please enable ~y~Risk Mode~w~ (under Settings) to use this feature!
Give wanted level_tooltip: Slowly gives the player a larger wanted level.
Send Attackers_tooltip: Send peds to attack the player.
Ram ~c~[Gentle]_tooltip: Rams the player with a car nice and slowly
Ram ~c~[Lethal]_tooltip: Rams the player with a car at a very high speed.
Give Money_tooltip: ~r~[Warning]~w~ Use at your own risk! This can only be used 2 times per session, or else you will be kicked from GTA:Online. Sorry for the inconveinence.
Give Rank_tooltip: Enter a rank between 1 and 8000 to give yourself! ~y~[Warning]~w~ Level changes are permenant, and you cannot go down levels once you have increased your rank.
Explode Vehicle_tooltip: This may kill anyone using this vehicle!
Detach all_tooltip: Detach all objects/entites that you have attached to this player.
Send SWAT_tooltip: These SWAT officers use tasers, not guns!
Make It Rain_tooltip: Teleports the entire lobby to a high position above your head, so that they all fall to their deaths around you.
Stealth Kill Lobby_tooltip: Silently kills everyone in the lobby.
~c~Explosion Loop_tooltip: This feature is ~r~[Locked]~w~ as it requires XenMenu VIP access! You may upgrade to VIP by visiting ~b~https://xenmenu.com
Clone session_tooltip: Creates a clone of every players ped.
Spawn In Vehicle_tooltip: Automatically places you inside a Vehicle you spawn.
Spawn Max Upgraded_tooltip: Automatically upgrades the Vehicle you have just spawned.
Spawn Air Vehicles Flying_tooltip: Any planes/helicopters that are spawned will be placed in the air.
Speedometer_tooltip: Displays your current vehicles speed in the bottom right of the screen.
Seatbelt_tooltip: Prevents you from falling off of bikes or fly thru the windshield.
~c~Cannot edit multipliers!_tooltip: Vehicle multipliers are currently broken! Please check back here in a future update, where this may actually work!
~c~Cannot edit multipliers!_tooltip1: You cannot edit the current vehicle multipliers because you are not the driver of this vehicle! Any multipliers set previously will not apply to this vehicle until you are the driver!
Vehicle Alpha_tooltip: Controls how transparent the Vehicle is (255 = not transparent).
Draw lasers_tooltip: Draw lazers coming from the front of your Vehicle to aid you when using Vehicle weapons.
Last vehicle_tooltip: Teleports you inside the last Vehicle you have used.
Custom coordinates_tooltip:
Allows you to teleport to a specific set of coordinates.
Enter the coordinates as numbers seperated by spaces, for example:
~b~100 100 1000
Weapon Upgrades_tooltip: Upgrade your weapons to MKII weapons and customise them.
Give Weapon All Attachments_tooltip: Adds all applicable attachments to the gun you are currently holding.
Give All Weapons Attachments_tooltip: Adds all applicable attachments to every gun you have.
Rubber Bullets_tooltip: Makes your bullets do no damage.
Silent Aimbot_tooltip: Automatically aims and shoots at players who aren't in passive mode.
Triggerbot_tooltip: Automatically shoots at the player you are aiming at.
Custom Impacts_tooltip: Change what happens when the bullet impacts with something (e.g. explode).
Weather_tooltip: Changes weather when the type is changed, or ~b~[SELECT]~w~ is pressed.
Funny vehicles_tooltip: Spawn funny vehicles such as a couch/toilet car, a driveable train, etc.
Unlock Dev Content_tooltip: Unlocks SCTV, clothing items such as the R* Developer T-Shirt, and probably some more stuff. This is not considered to be risky, but caution should be taken.
Auto Sync_tooltip: Toggles automatic syncing of the config.
Risk Mode_tooltip: Allows the use of potentially detected features.
Uninject_tooltip: You can reinject later without having to restart the game.
Show Vehicle Previews_tooltip: Toggles previews of the vehicle you will spawn to the right of the menu in the vehicle spawner menu.

Hancock Mode_tooltip:
Allows you to fly around the map like Superman.
Controls:
$<hancock_up> - Up
$<hancock_down> - Down
Vehicle Fly Mode_tooltip:
Controls:
$<veh_fly_forward> - Forward
$<veh_fly_backwards> - Backwards
$<veh_fly_left> - Turn left
$<veh_fly_right> - Turn right
$<veh_fly_pitch_up> - Pitch up
$<veh_fly_pitch_down> - Pitch down

$<veh_manager_tp_self> - Teleport self into vehicle
$<veh_manager_tp_vehicle> - Teleport vehicle to self
